<HEADLINE>
FT  04 FEB 94 / Audi chief expected to be forced out
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
   By CHRISTOPHER PARKES
</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>
   FRANKFURT
</DATELINE>
<TEXT>
