FT  04 FEB 94 / World News in Brief: Howard targets parents
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Home secretary Michael Howard outlined plans to fine parents up to Pounds
1,000 if their children do not comply with court orders. Slopping-out
deadline, Page 8
