FT  04 FEB 94 / World News in Brief: Kidnapper captured
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Russian security forces at Rostov-on-Don airport disarmed and captured a man
who seized three adults and two children at a kindergarten and demanded to
fly abroad. The hostages were seized early in the day from a town over the
border in Ukraine.
