330-340 programmes and improve its finances.
The government has put Aerospatiale on its list of state companies to be
sold into the private sector. However, it suggested recently that in the
near term letting industrial partners take a stake in the company was far
more likely than privatisation.
Aerospatiale has forecast a 1993 loss 'significantly less' than 1992's
FFr2.38bn.
